name: Raven Perched
category: Misc
footprint: 1x1
facing: yes
shadow: no
blocks_light: no
height: 0.6
placement: floor
room_types: graveyard-village, necropolis, crypt, tower-ruined, haunted-wood
typical_count: few
clusters_with: tombstone, crypt-entrance, crow-perched, statue-weeping, bone-pile
notes: Large raven on ground or perch — slightly bigger than a crow, darker, heavier body. Head south, alert gaze. Omen of death.
---
# === Faint body shadow ===
ellipse 0.50,0.62 0.20,0.05 fill #050204 0.30

# === Tail feathers (north, behind body — broader than crow) ===
